Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:05.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:08.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:09.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's going to be a hot day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss! Then I shall \Naccompany you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What has gotten into you, Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting up this early \Nin the morning all on your own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, heading off \Nto school of your own volition?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, to begin with, \Nsummer break started today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised? That was a great joke of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see, so that's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing it's summer break, \NI feel too restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I sleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I'm going to play \Nonline games, watch anime, draw manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have all the fun I want every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like her life is pretty similar, \Neven when she has school...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess she must be really happy, \Nconsidering how excited she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:24.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I can spend all my time \Nwith Hayate every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:32.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:35.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.85,0:01:38.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:41.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who is there to support his \Nmistress in all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:43.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:47.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This is about a boy who fights \Nand puts his life on the line for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:51.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait, I just transferred \Nand it's already summer break...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than greet my classmates \Nand duel at the kendo club,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did I do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:04.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:04.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:11.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:11.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:14.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:14.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:19.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:19.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:23.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:23.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:27.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:27.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:32.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:32.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:42.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:42.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:48.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:48.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:55.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:55.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:03:00.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:03:00.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:07.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:07.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:14.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:14.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Like Books, But Sing It \NGreat Palace of the Dragon King
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.44,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuou Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, summer break is pure bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can drink all the sake \NI want all day long!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of which, I can do \Nstuff like this all I want, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, doing nothing \Nis the ultimate form of luxury!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys, grade school \Nkids from the Showa Era?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We figured you would have time to kill, \Nso we came to invite you along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I appreciate the thought, \Nbut I'm busy right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go catch rhinoceros beetles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a tour on foot \Nof the thick woods around Fuji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Maria, do you know \Nany lethal techniques?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err... This is out of the blue. \NWhat is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I met some people I believe to be \Nfirst-rate butlers at Hakuou Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and according to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems first-rate butlers need \Nto know a lethal technique or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm thinking of learning some \Nkind of lethal technique, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that's what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, but why ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a hunch of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you look like someone \Nwho might know the Art of Assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But based on my hunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please toss your useless hunches \Nin the trash this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You know it, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, not you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd at least know the Five \NPoint Palm Exploding Heart Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! Don't turn me into \Na master of some fanboy technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, lethal techniques \Ncannot be learned so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer break is a great opportunity \Nand I'd like to master one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping there might be a book \Nto help me master a lethal technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A book...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would expect nothing \Nless of a Sanzenin library.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an amazing number of books!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which makes cleaning a real chore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But books are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you immerse yourself in a book, \Nsurrounded by all these books,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it truly makes you feel intellectual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's my Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, these must be the shelves \Nstocked exclusively for you, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is the one \Narea littered with manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're wrong, you know! \NI read other books, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all these video game guides.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reading really does \Nmake you feel intellectual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit mocking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be so fixated on lethal techniques...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot comprehend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:41.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate must want to \Nshow me how cool he can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall protect you with this \Nelegant technique of mine, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! This is impressive, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Hayate! I'll help you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look for books with clues \Nabout lethal techniques with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you very much, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! Lethal techniques!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:17.54,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Lethal Techniques in a Nutshell \NBook of Secret Sanzenin Techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like online karate classes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or like learning to draw manga \Nat a technical school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if there would be a book \Nthat could teach it to you so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:22.37,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Lethal Techniques in a Nutshell \NBook of Secret Sanzenin Techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Funnily enough, there actually might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lethal Techniques in a Nutshell \Nwith Colored Charts"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined there would be \Nsuch a useful sounding book!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:33.72,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Book of Secret Sanzenin Techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what do you suppose these \NSecret Sanzenin Techniques are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come to think of it, \NHimegami used to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Himegami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I hear his name come up \Nevery so often, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did I never tell you about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was Nagi's butler before you came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, various things happened \Nand he ended up leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this butler named Mr. Himegami \Nalso knew lethal techniques?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:08:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that perhaps \NMr. Klaus also knows such techniques?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to know \Nwhat my lethal technique is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, not really right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit playing around and go do work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if other butlers can do it, \Nthere's no way you couldn't, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, we're going to do special \Ntraining based on this book!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Y-Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me "Master"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Undefeated of the North, \NSouth, East, West, and Middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's a little too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scraped up my knee a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:49.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,There goes the myth of being undefeated, \Nnorth, south, east, west, and middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is hot outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, perhaps you shouldn't \Nstrain yourself too much
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take it easy in an air conditioned room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is for the sake \Nof your lethal technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Please instruct me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rarrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's start with something basic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Case 1 – the secret technique \Nfor when you're engulfed in flames."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it say? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, aren't there any secret techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for defeating the enemy {\i1}before{\i0} \Nyou become engulfed in flames?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, there doesn't seem \Nto be anything in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with a technique \Nfor such a dire situation is a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we give it a try anyway, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... "First, like \Nthe Conqueror of Century's End,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"command a body that does \Nnot burn, even in flames..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raoooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, the entire premise is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you can't do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Case 2 – the secret technique \Nfor when you get shoved off a cliff...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, let us do something about it \Nbefore getting shoved off a cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:48.90,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,The Secret Technique for Becoming \NMore Lovey-Dovey with the Guy You Like
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's n-n-n-nothing! It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:57.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What kind of secret \Ntechnique is this in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But I would love to master it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:01.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to master it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to skim through the whole book \Nto see if there's anything useful,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so would you mind letting me see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't! I decline! I absolutely refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wh-Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too soon for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I can't show you \Nwhat I can't show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss, it's dangerous to go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:30.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how do I get to be more lovey-dovey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:32.65,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire premise... \NThe entire premise is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss! In front! In front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rarrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could do something so embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:48.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rarrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Hayate, are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh... I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I was able to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:13.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I don't need \Nto rely on any secret techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate and I are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of this book is useless,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's got some serious stuff, \Ntoo, like things to watch out for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! If you work hard, \Nyou should be able to master these.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm going to learn \Na lethal technique this summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I better work hard for Hinagiku, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. \NFor Hinagiku, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For whom, did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Hinagiku is always \Nhelping me out in various ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I also promised her \Nthat I would show it to her
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once I mastered a super lethal technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promised? Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The book of secret techniques!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha... Ha... Hayate, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you please teach me a surefire \Ntechnique to soothe the Miss's temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that would require \Nquite a bit of training...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:27.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It would still be a long way off \Nbefore Hayate mastered a lethal technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please continue to watch every \Nepisode of "Hayate the Combat Butler"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watermelon seeds. Ptewy!\N({\u1}Su{\u0}ika no tane. {\u1}Peh{\u0}!)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight, Pero!\N({\u1}Pe{\u0}ro-san, fai{\u1}to{\u0}!)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss has run away from home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Members of the SP are following her, \Nso there's no need to worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it still makes me feel uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since everything the Miss does \Nis so incredibly abrupt
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the reasons for her actions \Nare never that clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:02.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I think the reason is undoubtedly you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! As the Miss's butler,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and also to get to the bottom \Nof her reasoning,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear! That Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about it being for Hinagiku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he mean to say that Hinagiku's \Nmore important to him than me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Hayate comes to love \NHinagiku more than me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't. You just can't! \NThis is wrong, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have Nagi, your precious girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Hinagiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only woman I can think of \Nthat I'm destined to be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! What's with you?! \NHayate, you stupid jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Hinagiku's so great anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku's just a little cute, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's good-natured and smart and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of which, she's an all-around \Nathlete, everyone trusts her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even I wish I could \Nbe a little like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to our bust sizes, \Nwe're about the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my grades are no worse than hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man, summer break's here, \Nbut I don't feel very happy somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Hayate's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Hayate was doing \Nat such an incredible mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world is that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have so many things I want to talk \Nto Hayate about and ask about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to hurry home and go to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all Hayate's fault to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...thieving hamster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you calling a thieving hamster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the trespassing hamster. \NThe lock-picking hamster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, I think I'd like \Nfor you to drop the "hamster" bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:01.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for starters, \Nit was a fateful reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that we've finally \Ncaught up with her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the Miss doing with Miss Nishizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. Is there any point \Nto this camouflage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought it might be \Nbetter to have than not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Hayate, \NI've been meaning to ask you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your relationship \Nwith that Miss Nishizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was my classmate at my old school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that makes sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could those two be talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:40.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would imagine it's about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're the owner of that mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you took Hayate in when \Nhe was rendered homeless?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of which, as a butler, \Nhe's living with you under one roof?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right. You have \Na problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urk... What an envious...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:58.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, that's not it. I feel so defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:02.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear God, you're so mean. \NThis is way unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, hamster. Don't ever \Ncome near my property again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I back down now, \NI'll remain the miserable defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my pride won't allow for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me! Fight me for Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I just happen \Nto be in a bad mood anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn the tables on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.92,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Karaoke BOX
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this place? As you \Ncan see, it's a karaoke booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I've heard of these places...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've ever \Nset foot in such an odd place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is smaller than our bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you spend hours and hours \Nin this cramped, dimly lit box,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you're not the heir \Nto the Mendou Zaibatsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like you'd still become \Nafraid of the dark and claustrophobic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, once we've ordered drinks, \Nwe're getting right to the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I won't mind ordering for you \Nif it's like just one item.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:01.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,An infinitely pointless attempt to show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll have a Shiun matcha green tea
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a tureen of foie gras from Périgord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I doubt they have those things...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they're going to karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? Oh, uh, p-pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, I've paid for \Nthe booth over here, so let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did Miss Nishizawa bring \Nthe Miss to a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate! Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this device?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you use it to punch in \Nnumbers to pick songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My! How amazing! \NYou can even adjust the pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, can you search \Nfor them in this book, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so thick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, since we're here anyway, \Nwould you like to try singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying, \NHayate? I could never.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know any of the \Nsongs that are popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm worried about Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can see their room from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and besides, I'd like to hear you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, if you go first, \NI'll sing at least one song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right. Then I shall go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.41,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,I Belong to You
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:33.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling me from somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:40.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, to see the score \Nwe've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! 35 points...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:51.44,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,You suck! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not surprising, considering \Nhow off key you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's your turn next!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:07.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,She's never karaoked in her life. \NThere's no way she'll sing well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:10.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, I was just warming up \Nand I didn't give it my best shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:13.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but once I get serious, I'll be sure to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:14.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch me, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:17.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you with my singing for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Get over here quick
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit mad
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:22.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Get over here quick
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,At mach speeds
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this sparkly aura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:29.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Socially reclusive Sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like Kirari Tsukishima to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:37.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you have to come flying right away
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:41.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, you just have to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:40.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:43.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because she's received education \Nfor the gifted since she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:45.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:47.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and naturally, included in that \Ncurriculum was voice training
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:49.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll be here soon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:50.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,from super top notch instructors, \Nand singing lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:53.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You may have forgotten, but Nagi \Nis technically a hyper refined young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:55.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be her first time at karaoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:58.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no way she'd lose \Nto a run-of-the-mill high school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.09,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, was that earlier singer Igant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about that? \NLooks like this fight is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! We're only getting started here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Singing is love! There's \Nno way I'm going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting! I'll pound you into the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.67,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(507,94)}Karaoke BOX
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:15.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Their karaoke match got heated up even more
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:15.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and continued late \Ninto the night. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sang a lot and I feel better now somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sniff. I can't believe I lose every round.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you want to use my credit card to pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! I'll treat you \Nfor something small like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be indebted \Nto a rival anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a term for when two \Nopponents are evenly matched?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.52,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, we have come to take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks. I'm surprised \Nyou knew where to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We received a call from your butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Hayate? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, hamster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, we'll compete \Nin something different!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you like. \NI'll turn the tables on you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to hurry home \Nand play games with Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer break has only just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:16.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But at that moment, \Nthe maid and the butler were...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:20.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lie to me, I'll see right through it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:23.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not blind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, why don't we stop around there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:25.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...still singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:28.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Romance, into your two hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:27.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, this was \Nthe first day of summer break...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do tomorrow for fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you guys plan \Nto keep staying here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:38.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the various people \Nenjoying it in their own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.77,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Strait is the Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, incidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it for the book report \Nand English composition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:45.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...we have one formidable \Ncharacter like her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:48.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids at home, make sure you \Nplan out your homework well, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:51.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, we'll be battling \Nminimum height restrictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:22:00.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Naida kokoro no ho ni kaze ga fuki-nuketetta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:22:00.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A breeze crossed the wilted sail of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:05.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimochi yureru soshite Lose My Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:05.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings waver and then I lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:08.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zutto kimi ga iru nara ii ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:08.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess if you'll always be here, it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:13.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sore mo waruku wa nai So I Go Together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:13.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not so bad, so I go together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:16.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenki-yohou nante nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:16.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Weather forecasts don't exist
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zenbu kibun-shidai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all mood-dependent
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:21.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanimo shinpai nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:21.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:24.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Makasete! Jiyuu-jizai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:24.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me! Perfectly free
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:26.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Keri-ageta kutsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:26.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,On the shoe that I kick up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:29.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Put A Wish" Zettai hareru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:29.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Put a Wish" it'll definitely clear up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:32.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kekka wa... I'm Looking At Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:32.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And the result is, I'm looking at nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:34.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mou ichido, yari-naoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:34.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time, a do-over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:38.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama ni wa kakete-miyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:38.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try betting once in a while
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:42.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee kimi ni yudanete-mitai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:42.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want to try entrusting you with it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:47.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sassou to kake-nukete To Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:47.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Running through gallantly, to fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:50.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Harema ga mieru The Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:50.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see a break in the weather, the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:51.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjiteta yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:51.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I had faith
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Soshite Make My Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I make my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:57.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sotto sashi-dasu kimi no te de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:57.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With the hand you quietly reach out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:02.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Muteki ni nareru kara So I Go Together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:02.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can become invincible, so I go together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:10.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshi ga kirei da ashita mo hareru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:10.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stars so beautiful, \Nit'll be clear again tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Isumi's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:29.72,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SIGN: Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.08,0:23:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I am Isumi Saginomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I was unable to make it \Ninto the main episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they have decided that \NI could be in this segment, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.53,0:23:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What should I talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Talk about this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.65,0:23:50.57,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(207,109)}Oh, dear
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.65,0:23:50.57,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(442.683,109)}Oh, dear
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... This song is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Isumi, keep talking that slow \Nand you're going to run out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.32,0:23:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi... Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.41,0:23:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.23,0:23:59.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, the butler \Nuniform just won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:01.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's this? \NAm I cross-dressing again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:19.47,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:04.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was thinking you can't be dressed \Nlike that for the amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.68,0:24:05.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Amusement park?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.62,0:24:07.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been reborn into this invincible body!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.42,0:24:10.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That debt-ridden butler's \Nno match for me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.42,0:24:13.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there, robot! \NWhose industrial spy are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.76,0:24:16.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Makimura! Not you, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.34,0:24:18.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.01,0:24:19.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Big Bother, Even for Peter".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.47,0:24:22.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've seen that robot \Nsomewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.47,0:24:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Big Bother, Even for Peter
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.16,0:24:24.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of justice \Nwill call forth a storm!
